						<summary>

						<p>On a rock in the Yemmikallu field in the village.</p>						

						<p>Circa 17th century.</p>						

						<p>This is dated the cyclic year Tāraṇa, Śrāvaṇa śu. 11. The details cannot be verified.</p>						

						<p>It records a gift of land to a <hi rend="italic">maṭha</hi> for the merit of his teacher Parvatadēva by <hi rend="italic">Mahārāja</hi> Immaḍi Barigeya Dēva-nāyaka. </p>						

